UID:84F63335-4BFB-4A39-8712-0BE63649BCE4
URL:www.axelradbeergarden.com/music
CREATED:20180827T173429Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us every Tuesday for a smooth and intimate setting of acou
 stic sounds from our hosts 'Nick and the Hits' and an acoustic-only Open Mi
 c from 7:30pm-9pm. \nWe provide the atmosphere and together we will all pro
 vide the sounds. \nOur Moody Tuesdays are entirely free and show starts at 
 7pm. The Open Mic is entirely acoustic and early sign up is available onlin
 e via our website. (www.axelradbeergarden.com/music)\nStop by and experienc
 e this at Axelrad’s Leisure Lounge located in our 2nd floor indoor stage.\n
 \nSchedule start 7pm\nSchedule end at 11pm
LAST-MODIFIED:20180827T173429Z
LOCATION:Axelrad Beer Garden\n1517 Alabama St\, Houston\, TX  77004\, Unite
