UID:6kqm8e1h6go38bb2c8p32b9k6oo68bb2ccpm2b9j75i6acj160q3aor360@google.com
URL:https://thelegacymusic.bandcamp.com/album/taylor-louis-the-legacy-ep
CREATED:20181209T043101Z
DESCRIPTION:The Legacy will be bringing their special mix of funk and RnB. 
 \nLocated in San Marcos\, Texas\, Taylor Louis & The Legacy is a high energ
 y hip-hop/RnB/Jazz that puts a modern and hip twist to their craft. The Ban
 d includes Taylor Louis on the keys and lead vocals\, Whitney Williams on b
 ass guitar and backup vocals\, and Marcus Alexander on the drums. The band 
 met as a result of the lead song-writer\, Taylor Louis\, was looking for a 
 band to perform his songs that he had written. After numerous jam sessions\
 , it was clear that the end result was a faucet for creativity that all mem
 bers contributed to. All the members bring their own sides to the plate\; M
 arcus Alexander brought a very sampled Hiphop feel\, Whitney Williams provi
 ded a more gospel feel to things\, while Taylor Louis brought a more soulfu
 l and jazz influenced sound. The end result was a three course meal that wa
 s completely original and a sound that was completely all of their own. The
  band currently gigs in San Marcos\, Houston\, and Austin. \nhttps://theleg
 acymusic.bandcamp.com/album/taylor-louis-the-legacy-ep
LAST-MODIFIED:20190515T180412Z
LOCATION:Axelrad Beer Garden\n1517 Alabama St\, Houston\, TX  77004\, Unite
 d States
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
