UID:copmccpmc9i3gbb3chj30b9k75hj0b9pcop3ebb268qmadhochi32opl64@google.com
CREATED:20181120T180432Z
DESCRIPTION:Axelrad Concert Series presents: Money Chicha - Free Show!\nMon
 ey Chicha is an Austin\, Texas based group featuring members of the Grammy-
 award winning Latin orchestra Grupo Fantasma and its offshoot funk outfit B
 rownout which performs a fuzzed-out\, reverb-drenched and percussion-heavy 
 style of music inspired by the sounds of Peru and Colombia in the 60s and 7
 0s. This style of music\, sometimes called “chicha” music\, is known for it
 s infectious Latin beat\, its psychedelic\, surf guitar pyrotechnics and it
 s melodies influenced by the indigenous culture of the Andes mountains. Thi
 s concert is free\, bring out your friends and family for this Sunday dance
  party!  Our Sunday Open Mic will be starting at 5pm-8:30pm!\n\nhttps://www
 .youtube.com/watch?v=z8hIKzaNi6U
LAST-MODIFIED:20190515T175145Z
LOCATION:Axelrad Beer Garden\n1517 Alabama St\, Houston\, TX  77004\, Unite
 d States
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:MUSIC: MONEY CHICHA + DJ YONDON OPEN MIC
TRANSP:OPAQUE
