BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART:20190914T180000Z
DTEND:20190914T210000Z
DTSTAMP:20260624T095702Z
UID:3mu823120i1f9pu4hnf5isn9av@google.com
CREATED:20190709T215759Z
DESCRIPTION:\nReserve entire inside area. Will get drink tickets and give t
 hem to each guest who donates books. They will be good for one free canned 
 bucket beer. \nWe love books.  We love brunch.  We love giving back to our 
 community.  At our Book\, Brunch\, and Benefit event we get to do all three
  at one of the coolest places to hang out in Houston.  So\, join us in the 
 beer garden for this awesome event!\n\nIt’s is free to attend\, all we ask 
 is that you bring a new or gently used book(s) of any genre\, for any age\,
  to donate to Madge Bush Transition Living Center – they provide transition
 al housing for homeless women and their children.  By donating you’ll also 
 receive a ticket for a beer (can selection only).  It’s a win-win!  And bri
 ng an extra to take-a-book/leave-a-book at the little library in the Axelra
 d Beer Garden.
LAST-MODIFIED:20190914T091911Z
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:HTX Books and Brunch
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
