 he Open Mic is entirely acoustic and early sign up is available online via 
 our website. (www.axelradbeergarden.com/music)\nStop by and experience this
  at Axelrad’s Leisure Lounge located in our 2nd floor indoor stage.\n\nSche
 dule start 7pm\nSchedule end at 11pm
