UID:6f1p0j6k1gfgptmesbsosc94st@google.com
CREATED:20190606T233759Z
DESCRIPTION:Join Gabby Meyer for Yoga at Axelrad the first Saturday & Sunda
 y of each month! The first weekend will be June 1st & June 2nd from 10:30-1
 1:30 am. Space is limited\, therefore participants are encouraged to regist
 er by 10 am day of event at www.yogawithgabby.net\n\nThis practice welcomes
  ALL levels. Join us for some yoga\, music\, and fun times! $5 per person i
 ncludes 1 hour of yoga\; doors will open at 10 am.\n\nGabby is an E-200 RYT
  Teacher who leads international retreats\, workshops\, events and classes 
 in Houston\, Texas. She is looking to bring yoga outside of a traditional s
 tudio setting & hopes to see you there! Namaste!
LAST-MODIFIED:20190606T233759Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Yoga w/ Gabby
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
