UID:0l7dqjs460iol3e56dt3cc5hs7@google.com
CREATED:20191008T190901Z
DESCRIPTION:HTX Market November 16th 10am - 3pm Raising money for Houston H
 eritage Society\nLoad in begins at 7-8am in Lawyer lot.\nLoad in at Axelrad
  at 10am\nThis will be a farmer's market/vendor market. They will have all 
 sorts of vendors that will be helping donate proceeds to their cause. They 
 will be doing workshops like Make Up\, CBD myths and truths and maybe candl
 e and bathbomb making. They will presale tickets for this before hand.\n\nW
 hat they need from us: space for a few vendors that need electricity and wo
 rkshops. They have asked us for a couple of cocktails to donate $1 from wit
 h Houston related names.\n\nWe will need to make sure Lawyer lot is clear t
 he night before.
LAST-MODIFIED:20191102T233330Z
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:HTX Market
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
