CREATED:20201018T051926Z
DESCRIPTION:We welcome families and all ages\, but promptly at 9pm from Sun
 day to Thursday\, we become 21+. If the movie begins before 8pm\, then peop
 le under the age of 21 are allowed to stay until the end of the movie only 
 if accompanied by a parent or guardian.<br>We value everyone's health and s
 afety and after consulting with our staff have have instituted temporary sy
 stems while social distancing is advised. We are encouraging making reserva
 tions to help with social distancing:&nbsp\;<a href="https://resy.com/citie
 s/hou/axelrad-beer-garden?fbclid=IwAR2-XVYxDW-4lcj6cViBCYe_g7do_21WdXxZcgy6
 uZITTIUWkgE57ZPOEUU">https://resy.com/cities/hou/axelrad-beer-garden</a>. I
 f the time slot that you want isn’t available\, you can select “NOTIFY ME” 
 and it will notify you when there is an opening in your desired time slot. 
 From there\, please read all of our new policies to ensure a safe visit for
  you and our staff.&nbsp\;&nbsp\;
LAST-MODIFIED:20201018T051926Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:MOVIE NIGHT - HELLRAISER (1987)
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
