 de the sounds. \nOur Moody Tuesdays are entirely free and show starts at 7p
 m. The Open Mic is entirely acoustic and early sign up is available online 
 via our website. (www.axelradbeergarden.com/music)\nStop by and experience 
 this at Axelrad’s Leisure Lounge located in our 2nd floor indoor stage.\n\n
