UID:2fptk95f5043enadoutkgekjsd@google.com
CREATED:20201018T052020Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for our first of three pumpkin carving/painting events 
 curated by our friends at Shop Local Market.<br>In order to promote everyon
 e's safety and health\, we will be limiting capacity for these events.<br>T
 o reserve your place\, send an email to drink@axelradbeergarden.com with a 
 guest count for your group (please specify # of children and adults). If in
  the event that spots fill up\, we can put you on a wait list\, you can mak
 e a reservation for a later time frame via&nbsp\;<a href="https://resy.com/
 cities/hou/axelrad-beer-garden?fbclid=IwAR3zQGVGOz0Z55PqNrKwP9hRLJfQ5jM2VxI
 Vd2_yClGYCTU5F3Z9kG9cVCE">https://resy.com/cities/hou/axelrad-beer-garden</
 a>\, or we can lock in a spot for you at one of the upcoming events.<br>*If
  the time slot that you want isn’t available\, you can select “NOTIFY ME” a
 nd it will notify you when there is an opening in your desired time slot. F
 rom there\, please read all of our new policies to ensure a safe visit for 
 you and our staff.<br>*While we will have some supplies\, you are more than
  welcome to bring your own as well!<br>***Reminder - We are 21+ at 9pm Sund
 ays to Thursdays.***&nbsp\;
LAST-MODIFIED:20201018T052020Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:PUMPKIN CARVING & PAINTING
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
