UID:0mf9j6tm07skc2dekge7c6lf2m@google.com
CREATED:20201018T052153Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for our last of three pumpkin carving/painting events c
 urated by our friends at Shop Local Market.<br>In order to promote everyone
 's safety and health\, we will be limiting capacity for these events.<br>To
  reserve your place\, send an email to drink@axelradbeergarden.com with a g
 uest count for your group (please specify # of children and adults). If in 
 the event that spots fill up\, we can put you on a wait list or you can mak
 e a reservation for a later time frame via&nbsp\;<a href="https://resy.com/
 cities/hou/axelrad-beer-garden?fbclid=IwAR17IM3cNmSevQzeNbCWjAut1UID62ePDZM
 jLR1Gidt6LFRZpQwBq-5zTE4">https://resy.com/cities/hou/axelrad-beer-garden</
 a>.<br>*If the time slot that you want isn’t available\, you can select “NO
 TIFY ME” and it will notify you when there is an opening in your desired ti
 me slot. From there\, please read all of our new policies to ensure a safe 
 visit for you and our staff.<br>*While we will have some supplies\, you are
  more than welcome to bring your own as well!<br>***Reminder - We are 21+ a
 t 9pm Sundays to Thursdays.***&nbsp\;&nbsp\;
LAST-MODIFIED:20201018T052153Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:PUMPKIN CARVING & PAINTING
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
