DESCRIPTION:This Halloween season\, we will be showing horror movies that a
 re more geared towards adults later at night on Sundays as well as All Hall
 ows' Eve!  The movie will start at 9pm (or a tee bit later as we have live 
 music prior to this event)!  Admission is ALWAYS FREE! \n\n(We welcome fami
 lies and all ages until 9pm on Mondays\, but promptly at 9pm we become 21+.
   If the movie begins before 8pm\, then people under the age of 21 are allo
 wed to stay only if accompanied by a parent or guardian.  
LAST-MODIFIED:20191004T204115Z
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Movie Night:  Halloween (1978)
TRANSP:OPAQUE
