CREATED:20210121T043431Z
DESCRIPTION:We welcome families and all ages\, but promptly at 9pm from Sun
 day to Thursday\, we become 21+. If the movie begins before 8pm\, then peop
 le under the age of 21 are allowed to stay until the end of the movie only 
 if accompanied by a parent or guardian.\n\nWe value everyone's health and s
 afety and after consulting with our staff\, we have instituted (temporary) 
 systems while social distancing is advised.\n     *Please do not rearrange 
 any furniture as it is set up specifically to promote a safe experience and
  it directly impacts the logistics for our team.\n     *Masks are mandatory
  at all times unless you are seated at your table.\n     *Walk-ins are welc
 ome / open seating\n     *Reservations can be made on certain days/time fra
 mes.\n\nFor more information -\n*Protocols: http://www.axelradbeergarden.co
 m/safety-protocols-and...\n*Reservations:\nhttp://www.axelradbeergarden.com
 /event-inquiries
LAST-MODIFIED:20210125T053035Z
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Movie Night: Hidden Figures
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
