CREATED:20210213T045328Z
DESCRIPTION:It's Studio Ghibli Month!\n\nCome out and enjoy dinner from a f
 ood vendor or Luigi's pizza and a movie on the big screen every Sunday!\n\n
 We welcome families and all ages\, but promptly at 9pm from Sunday to Thurs
 day\, we become 21+. If the movie begins before 8pm\, then people under the
  age of 21 are allowed to stay until the end of the movie only if accompani
 ed by a parent or guardian.\n\nWe value everyone's health and safety and af
 ter consulting with our staff\, we have instituted (temporary) systems whil
 e social distancing is advised.\n*Please do not rearrange any furniture as 
 it is set up specifically to promote a safe experience and it directly impa
 cts the logistics for our team.\n*Masks are mandatory at all times unless y
 ou are seated at your table.\n*Walk-ins are welcome / open seating\n*Reserv
 ations can be made on certain days/time frames.\nFor more information -\n*P
 rotocols: http://www.axelradbeergarden.com/safety-protocols-and...\n*Reserv
 ations:\nhttp://www.axelradbeergarden.com/event-inquiries
LAST-MODIFIED:20210314T072905Z
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Movie Night: Howl's Moving Castle
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
