UID:0igck7kir109837papmah0td44@google.com
CREATED:20210125T080659Z
DESCRIPTION:<br>Punchline Mondays is the BEST weekly stand-up comedy show y
 ou’ll find in the city of Houston! The show is FREE - So the laughs are on 
 us! Guaranteed the BEST way to start off your week. Come get these laughs e
 very Monday at Axelrad.<br><br>Show starts at 8pm in the garden\, under the
  tent (by Alabama St.)!<br><br>*Seating is set up to accommodate social dis
 tancing*<br><br>We value everyone's health and safety and after consulting 
 with our staff\, we have instituted (temporary) systems while social distan
 cing is advised.<br>&nbsp\; &nbsp\; &nbsp\; *Please do not rearrange any fu
 rniture as it is set up specifically to promote a safe experience and it di
 rectly impacts the logistics for our team.<br>&nbsp\; &nbsp\; &nbsp\; *Mask
 s are mandatory at all times unless you are seated at your table.<br>&nbsp\
 ; &nbsp\; &nbsp\; *Walk-ins are welcome.<br>&nbsp\; &nbsp\; &nbsp\; *Reserv
