DESCRIPTION:<br>We are celebrating badass women for Women's History Month!<
 br>Come out and enjoy dinner from a food vendor or Luigi's pizza and a movi
 e on the big screen every Sunday!<br>We welcome families and all ages\, but
  promptly at 9pm from Sunday to Thursday\, we become 21+. If the movie begi
 ns before 8pm\, then people under the age of 21 are allowed to stay until t
 he end of the movie only if accompanied by a parent or guardian.<br>We valu
 e everyone's health and safety and after consulting with our staff\, we hav
 e instituted (temporary) systems while social distancing is advised.<br>*Pl
 ease do not rearrange any furniture as it is set up specifically to promote
  a safe experience and it directly impacts the logistics for our team.<br>*
 Masks are mandatory at all times unless you are seated at your table.<br>*W
 alk-ins are welcome / open seating<br>*Reservations can be made on certain 
 days/time frames.<br>For more information -<br>*Protocols:&nbsp\;<a href="h
 ttp://www.axelradbeergarden.com/safety-protocols-and?fbclid=IwAR2wCc_z1aUzp
