UID:3u0m67o1ba99v88nrlmvnv8dht@google.com
CREATED:20201107T040041Z
DESCRIPTION:We welcome families and all ages\, but promptly at 9pm from Sun
 day to Thursday\, we become 21+. If the movie begins before 8pm\, then peop
 le under the age of 21 are allowed to stay until the end of the movie only 
 if accompanied by a parent or guardian.<br>We value everyone's health and s
 afety and after consulting with our staff\, we have instituted temporary sy
 stems while social distancing is advised. Please do not rearrange any furni
 ture as it is set up specifically to promote a safe experience and it direc
 tly impacts the logistics for our team. Masks are mandatory at all times un
 less you are seated at your table. We are now offering both bar and table s
 ervice.<br>Walk-ins are welcome and reservations can be made on certain day
 s/time frames.<br>To make a reservation\, check out&nbsp\;<a href="https://
 resy.com/cities/hou/axelrad-beer-garden?fbclid=IwAR2oNwxqUdH6eaCv8oi7bUh4iF
 ATQC6BBiQfZcKm19f3zdeNINgtPXS_R-c">https://resy.com/cities/hou/axelrad-beer
 -garden</a>. If the time slot that you want isn’t available\, you can selec
 t “NOTIFY ME” and it will notify you when there is an opening in your desir
 ed time slot. From there\, please read all of our new policies to ensure a 
 safe visit for you and our staff.&nbsp\;
LAST-MODIFIED:20201107T040041Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:MOVIE NIGHT - LION KING
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
