DESCRIPTION:<br>We welcome families and all ages\, but promptly at 9pm from
  Sunday to Thursday\, we become 21+. If the movie begins before 8pm\, then 
 people under the age of 21 are allowed to stay until the end of the movie o
 nly if accompanied by a parent or guardian.<br>We value everyone's health a
 nd safety and after consulting with our staff\, we have instituted temporar
 y systems while social distancing is advised. Please do not rearrange any f
 urniture as it is set up specifically to promote a safe experience and it d
 irectly impacts the logistics for our team. Masks are mandatory at all time
 s unless you are seated at your table. We are now offering both bar and tab
 le service.<br>Walk-ins are welcome and reservations can be made on certain
  days/time frames.<br>To make a reservation\, check out&nbsp\;<a href="http
 s://resy.com/cities/hou/axelrad-beer-garden?fbclid=IwAR1hvOxGfNLYnunDrc3_6F
 RSjaGlWoJ-ryM1C_Pjb7-xVsiVfaCbr3_F-rE">https://resy.com/cities/hou/axelrad-
 beer-garden</a>. If the time slot that you want isn’t available\, you can s
 elect “NOTIFY ME” and it will notify you when there is an opening in your d
 esired time slot. From there\, please read all of our new policies to ensur
 e a safe visit for you and our staff.
LAST-MODIFIED:20201101T234139Z
