CREATED:20210105T020319Z
DESCRIPTION:The theme for this month's movies is Fresh Starts with good ole
  Jim Carrey. Let's put 2020 in the past and move on to the better year ahea
 d of us!\n\nWe welcome families and all ages\, but promptly at 9pm from Sun
 day to Thursday\, we become 21+. If the movie begins before 8pm\, then peop
 le under the age of 21 are allowed to stay until the end of the movie only 
 if accompanied by a parent or guardian.\n\nWe value everyone's health and s
 afety and after consulting with our staff\, we have instituted temporary sy
 stems while social distancing is advised. Please do not rearrange any furni
 ture as it is set up specifically to promote a safe experience and it direc
 tly impacts the logistics for our team. Masks are mandatory at all times un
 less you are seated at your table.\nWalk-ins are welcome and reservations c
 an be made on certain days/time frames.\n\nIf you would like to make an off
 icial reservation\, check out https://resy.com/cities/hou/axelrad-beer-gard
 en.From there\, please read all of our new policies to ensure a safe visit 
 for you and our staff.
LAST-MODIFIED:20210105T021937Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Movie Night: The Truman Show
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
