DESCRIPTION:Vibe Haus\n\n1/29 @axelradhouston\n\nVIBE HAUS Radio\n\nVibe Ha
 us is a Retro Future sanctuary with an organic eclectic electronic sound. I
 nfluences of tracks from all genres and sub genres. With various heavy hitt
 ing Djs \,artist \,producers contributing to the Vibe Haus sound\, a cultur
 e centered around eclectic sounds and vibrations from different parts of th
 e galaxy. Featuring uptempo to downtempo tracks from global influences thes
 e Hi and Low Fidelity samples we create genre fusions from the past and pre
 sent leading us to the sounds of the future. \n\nLIVE FROM 2071 A.D.\n\nDJ 
 SETS\n\n@flovverheadd\n@djraqqcity\n@dfilogic\n@djnimbus\n@djcharleebrown\n
 \nLive Performance\n\n@leethemyth \n\nThe Premier of Original Comic Meta Ka
 izoku  Vol.1 by @leethemyth \n\nLee the Myth is on the run. Detective Kaige
  Armant and Mio Bain of the Interstellar Police are hot on the infamous spa
 ce pirates tracks and are close to catching him! Lee evades capture but suf
 fers a head injury rendering him unconscious. Before he was this space pira
 te bad-boy\, he was just a boy\, born into a world where he and people like
  him were considered abominations. Back then an event took place that chang
 ed him for the rest of his life and taught him a truth that has become a pa
 rt of his journey.\n\n@metakaizoku_ Vol. 1\n\nBrought to you by\n\n@thevibe
 shtx @wonkypower\n\nVisual Show\n\n@djcharleebrown\n@leethemyth\n@nguevarra
 _art\n\nA CURATED UNIVERSE\n\nRSVP\n@vibehausuniverse Link in Bio
LAST-MODIFIED:20230227T204826Z
SEQUENCE:2
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:MUSIC: VIBE HAUS FEATURING THE VIBES HTX
TRANSP:OPAQUE
X-APPLE-TRAVEL-ADVISORY-BEHAVIOR:AUTOMATIC
END:VEVENT
