UID:1E28ABAC-9B2B-4AB1-9E3B-A1729834BC3C
CREATED:20230804T184715Z
DESCRIPTION:Vibe Haus\n\nVIBE HAUS Radio\n\nVibe Haus is a Retro Future san
 ctuary with an organic eclectic electronic sound. Influences of tracks from
  all genres and sub genres. With various heavy hitting Djs \,artist \,produ
 cers contributing to the Vibe Haus sound\, a culture centered around eclect
 ic sounds and vibrations from different parts of the galaxy. Featuring upte
 mpo to downtempo tracks from global influences these Hi and Low Fidelity sa
 mples we create genre fusions from the past and present leading us to the s
 ounds of the future. \n\nLIVE FROM 2071 A.D.\n\nThe Premier of Original Com
 ic Meta Kaizoku  Vol.1 by @leethemyth \n\nLee the Myth is on the run. Detec
 tive Kaige Armant and Mio Bain of the Interstellar Police are hot on the in
 famous space pirates tracks and are close to catching him! Lee evades captu
 re but suffers a head injury rendering him unconscious. Before he was this 
 space pirate bad-boy\, he was just a boy\, born into a world where he and p
 eople like him were considered abominations. Back then an event took place 
 that changed him for the rest of his life and taught him a truth that has b
 ecome a part of his journey.\n\n@metakaizoku_ Vol. 1\n\nBrought to you by\n
 \n@thevibeshtx @wonkypower\n\nVisual Show\n\n@djcharleebrown\n@leethemyth\n
 @nguevarra_art\n\nA CURATED UNIVERSE
LAST-MODIFIED:20230804T184715Z
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:MUSIC: VIBE HAUS FEATURING THE VIBES HTX
TRANSP:OPAQUE
X-APPLE-TRAVEL-ADVISORY-BEHAVIOR:AUTOMATIC
END:VEVENT
