DTEND:20250728T000000Z
DTSTAMP:20260624T095702Z
UID:142t1b2i6m21agi6htvucb5hss@google.com
CREATED:20250618T094631Z
DESCRIPTION:<b>Music &amp\; Market curated by Mateo. 2pm-7pm. FREE. ALL AGE
 S</b><br><p dir="ltr">Mooty Mart: Hip Hop Thrift Market &amp\; Concert is l
 aunching at Axelrad Beer Garden\, bringing a fresh dose of culture\, beats\
 , and sustainable style to the city. This isn't just your average market\; 
 it's a vibrant community hub where discovering unique thrift treasures meet
 s the unmatched energy of live original hip-hop artistry. Imagine spending 
 your Sunday afternoon digging through racks for vintage finds\, then turnin
 g to catch some of Houston's hottest local DJs and artists tearing up the s
 tage – all under the colorful lights and laid-back vibes of Axelrad. Mooty 
 Mart is set to become your new favorite weekend destination\, celebrating l
 ocal talent and conscious consumption in one unforgettable experience.</p><
 p dir="ltr">Mark your calendars for our grand launch on Sunday\, July 27\, 
 2024\, at Axelrad Beer Garden! Mooty Mart is designed to uplift and connect
 \, providing a platform for local thrift vendors and small businesses along
 side a dynamic lineup of Houston's hip hop talent. Whether you're a seasone
 d thrifter\, a hip hop enthusiast\, or just looking for a fantastic way to 
 spend your weekend\, Mooty Mart promises an engaging and lively atmosphere 
 for everyone. Come for the finds\, stay for the beats\, and become a part o
 f Houston's newest cultural movement!</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250721T045401Z
SEQUENCE:3
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:(Music/Market | Main Stage): Mooty Mart: Hip-Hop Thrift Market and 
 Concert
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
