DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://www.tixtree.com/e/solar-flare-music-festival-2
 025-99f86c01950e">TICKETS &amp\; INFO HERE</a><br><strong>Solar Flare</stro
 ng> is back and burning brighter than ever. This two-day music festival\, h
 osted by Houston Music Classifieds\, brings together some of Houston's most
  exciting voices. This weekend is stacked with live music from 40+ local ac
 ts across two stages\, an artists market with incredible vendors\, and some
  very special surprises after midnight.<br><p>Friday's music runs from 5:30
  PM to midnight. Saturday kicks off at 3 PM and goes late. Just good people
  and nonstop music in the middle of Houston. <strong>The festival is all ag
 es (anyone under 18 MUST have an adult present) and everyone under 21 will 
 be allowed  until the last band ends at Midnight.</strong></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250717T011153Z
