 _blank">TICKETS &amp\; INFO HERE</a><br><strong>Solar Flare</strong> is bac
 k and burning brighter than ever. This two-day music festival\, hosted by H
 ouston Music Classifieds\, brings together some of Houston&#39\;s most exci
 ting voices. This weekend is stacked with live music from 40+ local acts ac
 ross two stages\, an artists market with incredible vendors\, and some very
  special surprises after midnight.<br><p>Friday&#39\;s music runs from 5:30
  PM to midnight. Saturday kicks off at 3 PM and goes late. Just good people
  and nonstop music in the middle of Houston. <strong>The festival is all ag
 es (anyone under 18 MUST have an adult present) and everyone under 21 will 
 be allowed  until the last band ends at Midnight.</strong></p>
